ing the surgery, Dr. Erdur will conduct a follow-up examination, discussing all details about your medications, any restrictions, and so on. After this, you will be discharged from the hospital.<\/p>\n<h2><b>STEP 4: CONTROL EXAMINATION <\/b><\/h2>\n<p>During the first week post-surgery, you will return to the clinic for a control examination, during which your nasal cast and splints will be removed. After this, you&#8217;re free to return to your home country. We will also conduct online follow-up examinations. Remember, you can contact us anytime should you need assistance.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>STEP 1: FIRST CONTACT After your initial contact with our clinic via social media or WhatsApp, we will schedule a video call to provide you with more details about the surgical process. During this call, you&#8217;ll have the opportunity to speak with Dr. Burak Erdur, ask any questions, and express your expectations regarding the surgery. [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":584,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[4],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/burakerdur.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/580"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/burakerdur.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/burakerdur.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/burakerdur.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/burakerdur.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=580"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/burakerdur.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/580\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":581,"href":"https:\/\/burakerdur.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/580\/revisions\/581"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/burakerdur.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/584"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href"